data.title: The Invisible Man by H.G. Wells (English) Paperback Book 9781461152392
data.meta_description: The Invisible Man of the title is Griffin, a scientist who theorises that if a person's refractive index is changed to exactly that of air and his body does not absorb or reflect light, then he will be invisible.
